data.description: Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful house your home. Built one year ago and NO specials! Situated on a large corner lot, you will appreciate the privacy and location of this newly built slab on grade. With insulated concrete forms, heated floors in the home and garage, open layout with vaulted ceilings, this energy efficient home will impress you. Offering four bedrooms, two bathrooms, three stall heated/finished garage, a beautiful kitchen with a pantry and buffet, a front porch and back patio!
